            "answer_text": "Same, but mainly people use 'car' in written and formal languages, not spoken languages or letters. You will find 'car' common in argumentative essays or non-fictions. Another important thing to note, 'car' is usually placed in the beginning of the sentence, unlike 'parce que' which can be placed in the beginning or middle of the sentence. ",
